{"title":"挂载多个云盘","uid":"a277eccdd9dade650bb983b75b36c716","slug":"挂载多个云盘","date":"2023-05-03T12:57:49.000Z","updated":"2023-05-03T16:50:39.443Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/挂载多个云盘.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/medias/1682924501962.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"简介\"><a href=\"#简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"简介\"></a>简介</h2><p><strong>介绍一款能挂载多种网盘的神器AList</strong></p>\n<p><strong>AList：支持多种存储的目录文件列表程序，支持 web 浏览与 webdav，后端基于<code>gin</code>，前端使用<code>react</code>。</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"支持的存储\"><a href=\"#支持的存储\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"支持的存储\"></a>支持的存储</h2><ul>\n<li>本地存储</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.aliyundrive.com/\">阿里云盘</a></li>\n<li>OneDrive &#x2F; Sharepoint（<a href=\"https://www.office.com/\">国际版</a>, <a href=\"https://portal.partner.microsoftonline.cn/\">世纪互联</a>,de,us）</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://cloud.189.cn/\">天翼云盘</a> (个人云, 家庭云)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/\">GoogleDrive</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.123pan.com/\">123 云盘</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pc.woozooo.com/\">蓝奏云</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Xhofe/alist\">Alist</a></li>\n<li>FTP</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.mypikpak.com/\">PikPak</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://shandianpan.com/\">闪电盘</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/cn/s3/\">S3</a></li>\n<li>WebDav</li>\n<li>Teambition（<a href=\"https://www.teambition.com/\">中国</a>，<a href=\"https://us.teambition.com/\">国际</a>）</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.mediatrack.cn/\">分秒帧</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://yun.139.com/\">和彩云</a> (个人云, 家庭云)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://disk.yandex.com/\">Yandex.Disk</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/\">百度网盘</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pan.quark.cn/\">夸克网盘</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pan.xunlei.com/\">迅雷云盘</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"系统挂载云盘\"><a href=\"#系统挂载云盘\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"系统挂载云盘\"></a>系统挂载云盘</h2><p><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/alist-org/alist/releases/\">Alist 开源项目地址</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.raidrive.com/\">raidrive网址</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://potplayer.daum.net/\">potplayer播放器网址</a></strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"下载Alist\"><a href=\"#下载Alist\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下载Alist\"></a>下载Alist</h2><p><strong>有三种安装方式：一键脚本安装，手动安装，docker镜像</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://alist.nn.ci/zh/guide/\">Alist官方文档</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>推荐用脚本安装，方便</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">#自定义路径\ncurl -fsSL &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;alist.nn.ci&#x2F;v3.sh&quot; | bash -s install &#x2F;root</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98/image-20230503223713159.png\" alt=\"image-20230503223713159\"></p>\n<p><strong>启动Alist</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">systemctl start alist\n#设置自启动\nsystemctl enable alist</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"演示\"><a href=\"#演示\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"演示\"></a>演示</h2><h3 id=\"阿里云盘\"><a href=\"#阿里云盘\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"阿里云盘\"></a>阿里云盘</h3><p><strong>访问<a href=\"http://your_ip:5244/%EF%BC%8C%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%AE%8Calist%E5%90%8E%E7%BB%99%E7%9A%84username%E5%92%8Cpassword\">http://YOUR_IP:5244/，输入安装完alist后给的username和password</a></strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>YOUR_IP  你的服务器IP</p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98/image-20230503212014697.png\" alt=\"image-20230503212014697\"></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>为了方便，登录后建议改账号和密码</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>添加云盘</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98/image-20230503224912663.png\" alt=\"image-20230503224912663\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98/image-20230503225414510.png\" alt=\"image-20230503225414510\"></p>\n<p>要用app扫二维码来获取刷新令牌——&gt;<strong><a href=\"https://alist.nn.ci/tool/aliyundrive/request.html\">刷新令牌获取</a></strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"迅雷云盘\"><a href=\"#迅雷云盘\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"迅雷云盘\"></a>迅雷云盘</h3><p><strong>挂载路径：&#x2F;迅雷云盘</strong></p>\n<p><strong>用户名和密码则是你迅雷的账户密码</strong></p>\n<p><strong>直接点保存，旁边会出现警告，复制href&#x3D;” “ 双引号里的网址（如果警告里的显示不全，按F5刷新在点保存，直到能看到click here就行，这样就能复制全网址了）</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98/image-20230503232035282.png\" alt=\"image-20230503232035282\"></p>\n<p><strong>用edge浏览器打开复制的网址，复制captcha_token里的值，粘贴到验证码里</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98/image-20230503233650864.png\" alt=\"image-20230503233650864\"></p>\n<p><strong>在管理页面的左边点主页就能看到你挂载的云盘了，在主页下面的点管理又能回到管理页面</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98/image-20230503235226850.png\" alt=\"image-20230503235226850\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"挂载到本地\"><a href=\"#挂载到本地\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"挂载到本地\"></a>挂载到本地</h3><p><strong>下载RaiDrive</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98/196048054-086b91ee-a575-4d3d-9a51-53686a00e85f.png\" alt=\"196048054-086b91ee-a575-4d3d-9a51-53686a00e85f\"></p>\n<p><strong>挂载完后在本地磁盘就能看得到了</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"用PotPlayer播放器在线观看\"><a href=\"#用PotPlayer播放器在线观看\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"用PotPlayer播放器在线观看\"></a>用PotPlayer播放器在线观看</h3><p><img src=\"/../images/%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98/image-20230504001622503.png\" alt=\"image-20230504001622503\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98/image-20230504001653256.png\" alt=\"image-20230504001653256\"></p>\n<p><strong>效果</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98/image-20230504001150591.png\" alt=\"image-20230504001150591\"></p>\n","text":"简介介绍一款能挂载多种网盘的神器AList AList：支持多种存储的目录文件列表程序，支持 web 浏览与 webdav，后端基于gin，前端使用react。 支持的存储 本地存储 阿里云盘 OneDrive &#x2F; Sharepoint（国际版, 世纪互联,de,us）...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":961,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"orangepi","slug":"orangepi","count":3,"path":"api/categories/orangepi.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"arm64","slug":"arm64","count":4,"path":"api/tags/arm64.json"},{"name":"随便玩玩","slug":"随便玩玩","count":1,"path":"api/tags/随便玩玩.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">简介</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%9A%84%E5